1
00:00:01,670 --> 00:00:03,630
Sorry.

2
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:08,930
What's going on?

3
00:00:09,630 --> 00:00:13,510
Wow, that sobered me right up.
Are you two having fun?

4
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,850
Oh, no!
It was just an accident.

5
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:17,310
Huh? Yuki?

6
00:00:18,810 --> 00:00:20,150
He's asleep.

7
00:00:20,150 --> 00:00:21,520
Yeah...

8
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:24,980
Sorry for the wait.

9
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:28,110
Hehe, he's sleeping so soundly.

10
00:00:31,660 --> 00:00:34,580
Makoto-kun,
why don't you cover Yuki with a blanket?

11
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:36,370
Shouldn't you be the one to do that, Natsu-san?

12
00:00:36,370 --> 00:00:38,040
I think he'd be happier
if his girlfriend did it.

13
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:40,080
Besides, he was getting jealous just now.

14
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:46,590
If that's the case, then it's all the more reason
for you to do it, Makoto-kun.

15
00:00:47,510 --> 00:00:49,090
Go on.

16
00:00:55,970 --> 00:01:00,140
Because he wasn't jealous of me.
He was jealous of you, Makoto-kun.

17
00:01:00,140 --> 00:01:02,190
What do you mean?

18
00:01:02,190 --> 00:01:04,360
Aren't you two a couple?

19
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:06,190
Nope.

20
00:01:06,190 --> 00:01:08,900
Huh? You're not his girlfriend?

21
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:13,070
I knew it.
Why didn't that guy Yuki tell you?

22
00:01:13,070 --> 00:01:16,160
But you two were acting so close just now...

23
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:18,160
And you're always together at school.

24
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,790
That's because we were putting on an act.

25
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:24,830
Great. That means
we really do look like a couple, then.

26
00:01:24,830 --> 00:01:28,300
You don't just look like a couple, you're perfect for each other.

27
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,130
Don't worry.

28
00:01:30,130 --> 00:01:33,130
Yuki and I are just a fake couple.

29
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,140
A fake couple?
